# Never send secrets or heavy local artifacts into the build context.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/.venv
**/venv
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/out
**/__pycache__
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.db
**/*.db-wal
**/*.db-shm
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.mypy_cache
.git
.gitignore
**/*.log
docs/screenshots
